  energy&rdquo\; (<em>Entertainment Weekly</em>). <br /><br />Directed by M
 arc Bruni (<em>Beautiful: The Carole King Musical</em>)\, this story of ex
 travagance and longing features choreography by Dominique Kelley (<em>So Y
 ou Think You Can Dance</em>)\, a book by Kait Kerrigan (<em>The Mad Ones</
 em>) and a jazz- and pop-influenced original score by Jason Howland (<em>L
 ittle Women</em>) and Nathan Tysen (<em>Paradise Square</em>).</p>
LOCATION:Broadway Theatre\, 1681 Broadway\, New York NY 10019
END:VEVENT
